<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1802774-do-you-consider-this-to-be-a-true-memoir">Do you consider this to be a true memoir?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1802774'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F58174.Promise_at_Dawn">like</a></span>

