<div id="review_1764285731" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1764285731" />
    <a title="Marina Sofia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9106945-marina-sofia"><img alt="Marina Sofia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1337757282p2/9106945.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1764285731?book_show_action=true">Sep 24, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marina Sofia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marina Sofia" href="/user/show/9106945-marina-sofia">Marina Sofia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback " href="/book/show/119003.La_promesse_de_l_aube">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1764285731" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11336613040446398183">Oh, wow! One of the funniest and yet most touching personal memoirs I&apos;ve ever read. I&apos;m certainly going to read more by this author.</span>
  <span id="freeText11336613040446398183" style="display:none">Oh, wow! One of the funniest and yet most touching personal memoirs I've ever read. I'm certainly going to read more by this author.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11336613040446398183" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

