        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer68136946" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14679824977232571649">This book was just amazing. I never would have chosen to read it on my own, but it was the example of modern French literature in a course that I took. Romain Gary is an interesting character all on his own in real life. This book includes parts of his autobiography, but mixed in with fiction so that it&apos;s impossible to tell when is real and what is not. It&apos;s impossible to not be moved by the end of this book and it&apos;s one that I will treasure. <br/><br/>If possible, I recommend reading the original French </span>
  <span id="freeText14679824977232571649" style="display:none">This book was just amazing. I never would have chosen to read it on my own, but it was the example of modern French literature in a course that I took. Romain Gary is an interesting character all on his own in real life. This book includes parts of his autobiography, but mixed in with fiction so that it's impossible to tell when is real and what is not. It's impossible to not be moved by the end of this book and it's one that I will treasure. <br /><br />If possible, I recommend reading the original French version.</span>
