<span id="freeTextContainer14099547405276212">At least twenty years have elapsed since I read this. Mr. Gary&apos;s mother was an extraordinary woman and their relationship was close, and unusual. Although it is written in a somewhat romantic, dramatic manner, it is nonetheless one of the most unforgettable memoirs I have ever read. As I write this, I&apos;m promising myself to read it again.</span>
  <span id="freeText14099547405276212" style="display:none">At least twenty years have elapsed since I read this. Mr. Gary's mother was an extraordinary woman and their relationship was close, and unusual. Although it is written in a somewhat romantic, dramatic manner, it is nonetheless one of the most unforgettable memoirs I have ever read. As I write this, I'm promising myself to read it again.</span>
