        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer563929421" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6809189354068173100">Beautiful book. So full of optimism...but also full of lies. Yes, Gary became everything his mother wanted and more, but then he killed himself. This is why I am removing one star--the main question still remains unanswered: if Mr Gary&apos;s life was so wonderful and everything worked out in the end, why did he decide to kill himself?</span>
  <span id="freeText6809189354068173100" style="display:none">Beautiful book. So full of optimism...but also full of lies. Yes, Gary became everything his mother wanted and more, but then he killed himself. This is why I am removing one star--the main question still remains unanswered: if Mr Gary's life was so wonderful and everything worked out in the end, why did he decide to kill himself?</span>
